@page "/privacy-policy"

<PageTitle>Privacy Policy — @Tenant.StoreName</PageTitle>

<div class="legal-page">

    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <span class="legal-updated">Last updated: January 2025</span>

    <div class="legal-highlight">
        <p>We value your privacy. This policy explains what personal data we collect, why we collect it, and how we protect it. By using our store you agree to the practices described below.</p>
    </div>

    <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>When you place an order or create an account we collect:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Full name and email address</li>
        <li>Delivery address and phone number</li>
        <li>Order history and preferences</li>
        <li>Device and browser information for security purposes</li>
    </ul>
    <p>We do not store payment card details. All payments are processed by our secure payment provider.</p>

    <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p>We use your data solely to:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Process and fulfil your orders</li>
        <li>Send order confirmations and delivery updates</li>
        <li>Respond to your support inquiries</li>
        <li>Improve our store and product offering</li>
        <li>Send promotional emails — only if you opt in</li>
    </ul>
    <p>We never sell, rent, or trade your personal information to third parties.</p>

    <h2>3. Cookies</h2>
    <p>We use essential cookies to keep your session active and remember your language preference. We do not use advertising or tracking cookies from third parties.</p>

    <h2>4. Data Sharing</h2>
    <p>Your data may be shared only with:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Courier and delivery partners — name, phone, and address to fulfil shipments</li>
        <li>Payment processors — for secure transaction handling</li>
        <li>Hosting providers — who store data on secured servers under strict confidentiality agreements</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>5. Data Retention</h2>
    <p>We retain your order data for up to 3 years for accounting and warranty purposes. You may request deletion of your account and personal data at any time by contacting us.</p>

    <h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
    <p>You have the right to:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Access the personal data we hold about you</li>
        <li>Correct inaccurate information</li>
        <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
        <li>Withdraw consent for marketing communications at any time</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>7. Security</h2>
    <p>We use industry-standard encryption (HTTPS/TLS) for all data in transit. Access to customer data is restricted to authorised personnel only.</p>

    <h2>8. Contact</h2>
    <p>For any privacy-related questions or requests, please contact us at <a href="tel:@Tenant.ContactPhone">@Tenant.ContactPhoneDisplay</a>.</p>

</div>
